

**Matt hab wo chum masmak mo g si shondal **

1 Jiosh o si s-hemajim ab t-mahkch g gewkdag ahchim matt ab i t-hemakoch g Jesus Christ wehm. Kuni heg hekaj m-ahgid mapt s-gegokim wo himad g e-chikpan wehhejed. 2 Muꞌi hemajkam ani ha mihshmad m-kaichudch. Kupt ahpi epai wo ha mashcha hegam mat am wo i e nakog k haꞌijj epai wo ha mashcha ihda. 

3 Neh, bapt masma wo e shoꞌigch mat g shondal am hab junihidch g e-chikpan am wehhejed g Jesus Christ. 4 S-mahch ap mat g shondal wehs hab wo junihid hegai mat g uhgchugaj ab wo cheha ch pi haꞌichu wo hiwigi mas wo shohbi. Kupt ahpi hab waꞌap wo masmak am wehhejed g Jiosh. 

5 S-mahch ap mat g s-melidkam pi ab hu wo bei g e-gehgewi heg hi wa mat am hab wo junihid g ha-chehanig. Kupt ahpi hab waꞌi masma wo bei g e-gehgewi mapt am Jiosh tatchui oidk hab wo e junihid. 

6 Hegai mo si chikpan g e-esha at wehpeg ab wo ui g e-oda mat wo bai. Kupt ahpi hab waꞌap ab haꞌichu wo i nei am chikpank g Jiosh wehhejed. 

7 Am g i oidahim ihda mani m-ahgid. T g Jiosh am wo i m-wehmt mapt wo s-amich. 

8 Jesus Christ o hab waꞌap d oꞌodham ch ab s-ap nakog g shoꞌigdag. T g Jiosh ab uhpam i wuhshad heg i dahm mat muh. Do ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahga mani am ahgachug. Kupt am wo oidahid mat haschu ab nako g Christ ch s-ap ab wo nako g e-shoꞌigdag. 9 Ni ahni hab waꞌap ni-shoꞌigchud am ahgachugch ihda s-kehg haꞌichu ahga hask mam ep ge ni-wulshch g e hukshchim wapainomikaj hab masma mantp d si pi ap hemajkam. K wabshaba g Jiosh neꞌoki pi e wulshch. 10 Am ani wabsh i ni-dagitokch mantp haschu ab wo i nako ha wehhejed hegam mat g Jiosh am i apꞌech mat wo e doꞌibia. Idam at ab wo i s-wohoch g haꞌichu t-ahga ab amjed g Jesus Christ. T g Jiosh chum hekid ab wo si has ha elidad. 11 Do si wohokam ihda hab ha-cheꞌi: 

Chum att hekid d wo dodakamk g Christ wehm mach hedai ab i t-dagitokch wui nat pi t-wehhejed muh. 

12 T heg ab wo t-hiwigi matt wo i wehmt am eda g kownaltaligaj ahchim matt an wo uꞌukchid g t-wohochudadag am t-shoꞌigdag ed. 

T wabshaba im hu hab wo i e juh ab ha amjed hegam mat wo dagito g e-wohochudadag. 

13 Hemho wa at am hab wo juh mo has i kaij. 

Kut pi gam hu hab wo i e juh ab t-amjed, heg hi wa mattp wo dagito g t-wohochudadag. 

**Mat has masma d wo s-ap chikpandamk **

14 Am g i ha chegitochud ihda mani wa m-ahgid k ab ha shohbid g Jiosh gewkdagkaj mat pi wabsh pehegi wo neneokad ch pi wo e cheggiad. Id at wo ha padch hegam mat wo kaiha. 15 Am g si i e nakog mapt d wo si s-ap piongajk g Jiosh ch si s-ap am wo ha mashchamad g Jiosh wohokam mapt pi wo shaꞌi si e elidad. 

16-18 Haꞌi at dagito g wohokam k ha mashcham mat heki hu ab i wuwha g koꞌi muhkig amjed. Gohkajj idam mo id hekaj ha iattogid o d Hymanaeus ch Phyletus. K g ha-mashchama padchud g ha-wohochudadag hab masma mat g pi kehg hihwdag wo em-cheawuagi. Pi g ha wehm aꞌagad g ha-mashchama. Gm at hu hab wo i m-juh ab amjed g Jiosh. 19 T wabshaba g Jiosh s-wihnam shondad g e-neꞌoki mat pi hedai wo shaꞌi gawul juh. K an oꞌohanas: 

Jiosh o s-ha mahch mo hedai woho ab s-wohochud. *Numbers 16:5 * 

K an ep oꞌohanas: 

Matp hedai hab wo chei mo d Jiosh hemajkamga k hemho wa gam hu hab wo i e juh ab amjed g pi apꞌekam. *Psalm 34:14 * 

20 Neh, matp hems am wo haꞌichugk g nahnko mahs hohashahaꞌa am s‑kais kih ed. Tp hems haꞌi d wo ohlak ch haꞌi d wo plahtak ch haꞌi d wo uhsk ch haꞌi d wo bidk. Kut wo e hekaj hegam mo s‑namkig ha wehhejed g s‑has hahaꞌichu. T g pi namkigchu wabsh chum has masma wo e hekaj. 21 Pegih, t g Jiosh hab wa masma si s‑has haꞌichukaj wo t‑hekaj mattp hedai wo t‑kegchudch ab amjed g pi apꞌekam natt pi wo t‑nahtokch ch wo i t‑gawulkadch wehhejed. 

22 Pegih, pi g am i e dagito pi apꞌekam ch ed k am s‑ap wo i e gewkadch s‑apꞌekam k ed ch am hab wo junihid mapt haschu wo ha ahgi ch wo si pihk e elidad wehs ha hekaj ch wo si s‑ap e tahtkkad ab ha wui g e‑wehm wohochuddam. T hegam mo ab ihm g Jiosh ch s‑ap haꞌichu chegito m‑wehm hab wo masmak. 23 Bant ep wo chei mapt pi wo ha neꞌowi hegam mat wabsh wo has hu kaijjid ch pi e mahch ch e neꞌowin. S‑mahch ap mat id am wabsh wo ha uꞌapa kawhaina ch ed. 24 Jiosh pionag at pi wo chum ha kawhainad ch wabsh wo si s‑hemajimak ab wehs ha wui ch wo si s‑ap ha mashchamad 25 ch si s‑hemajim wo ha shohbidad hegam mat ab wui wo gegokiwua ch wo ha mashchamad. Tp hems ab wo ha mah g Jiosh g apꞌedag mat wo s‑ohhod g pi ap e‑chegitoi k ab wo s‑mai g wohokam. 26 T hab masma uhpam wo bei g s‑ap e‑chegitoidag k wo e doꞌibia ab amjed g Jiawul. 

